B.Na=new A.hW("O CEI Aurora oferece uma forma diferente de ensino. Acreditamos que crian\xe7a \xe9 um ser \xfanico e especial, cheia de imagina\xe7\xe3o, sonhos, energia e vigor. A forma como ela aprende do mundo \xe0 sua volta deve ser, tamb\xe9m, repleta de fantasia e vitalidade, tornando o processo de aprendizado muito mais interessante.",null,B.dO,B.aw,null)
B.Nb=new A.hW("Acreditamos que as crian\xe7as aprendem brincando, explorando, inventando e fazendo. A experi\xeancia \xe9 o melhor e mais competente professor. Atrav\xe9s das brincadeiras as crian\xe7as exploram o mundo, n\xe3o existindo uma resposta certa ou errada, apenas um processo de aprendizagem.",null,B.dO,B.aw,null)
B.Nc=new A.hW("Empatia Produtos Psicopedag\xf3gicos is a brazilian company, and since its founding has been dedicated to providing a safe and engaging space for children and adults to learn and grow.\n\nOur journey began with the launch of Jogo Empatia, an innovative emotional intelligence card game designed to foster empathy and understanding. This initial product featured a single box with 3 different types of cards: feelings, what's important, and choices.\n\nIn 2020, we launched two new boxes, introducing 6 new types of cards: areas of life, thoughts, paths of self-discovery, body awareness, body parts, and bodily sensations.\n\nAll of the cards were designed to be modular, allowing users to mix and match cards to create unique and personalized learning experiences.\n\nIn 2024, we are excited to bring the essence of our physical products to the digital world with the launch of the Empatia app. This app version of our beloved card game continues our mission of fostering emotional intelligence and personal growth, providing a modern and accessible platform for users to explore and develop their skills.\n\nAnd after the launch of the Empatia app, in collaboration with mental health professionals, we developed the Empatia Track app to assist and support everyone seeking to understand their mental health.",null,B.dO,B.aw,null)
B.Nd=new A.hW("O Espa\xe7o de brincar no Centro de Educ. Infantil Aurora valoriza a express\xe3o e a socializa\xe7\xe3o retomadas pela equipe da escola, com apoio da fam\xedlia e da comunidade, e gera espa\xe7os para a estrutura\xe7\xe3o de ambientes de livre explora\xe7\xe3o, onde o brincar pode ter lugar simult\xe2neo a outros, necess\xe1rios para a educa\xe7\xe3o da crian\xe7a pequena.",null,B.dO,B.aw,null)
B.Kd=new A.p(!0,B.it,null,null,null,null,16,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
B.Ne=new A.hW("Developed by\nEmpatia Produtos Psicopedag\xf3gicos",null,B.Kd,B.aw,null)
